snippet.title: The Sims 4 Cats & Dogs: Veterinarian Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Build and run a veterinary clinic to take care of neighborhood pets while advancing your Sim's vet career.

Learn more about The Sims 4 Cats & Dogs Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/35550

Be in control of daily operations, from the services offered to how much you charge for them. Diagnose and treat a variety of ailments with simple medications or critical surgeries! 

Available November 10, 2017 on PC/Mac
